Package jetbrains.mps.openapi.editor.cells

Interface DefaultSubstituteInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SubstituteInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanSPropertySubstituteInfo, DefaultSChildSubstituteInfo, DefaultSReferenceSubstituteInfo, EnumSPropertySubstituteInfo, SChildSubstituteInfo, SEmptyContainmentSubstituteInfo, SPropertySubstituteInfo, SReferenceSubstituteInfo, SReferenceSubstituteInfoSmartReferenceDecorator
    public interface DefaultSubstituteInfo
extends SubstituteInfo
    This is a marker interface exposing the fact that corresponding SubstituteInfo was created by default editor logic, means there was no custom actions specified by user.

    This marker interface can be used at runtime to replace one "default" SubstituteInfo with another "default" one while building EditorCell tree.

    No custom actions will be replaces.
